Package domain

Class Partition

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Partition
  • public class Partition
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a partition within a KenKen board. A partition defines a region of cells and specifies an operation to be performed on the numbers within those cells. This class also holds the expected result of the operation.
